General.Name: Nickelsearch Ltd
General.Description: NickelSearch Limited operates as a nickel sulphide exploration company in Australia. Its flagship project is the 100% owned Carlingup project covering and area of 108 square kilometers consisting of 8 mining and 7 exploration licences located in the Ravensthorpe Greenstone Belt, Western Australia. The company was formerly known as Australasian Mining Limited and changed its name to NickelSearch Limited in August 2021. NickelSearch Limited was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Osborne Park, Australia.
